PrecisRegulations Amending the BOATING RESTRICTION REGULATIONS by harmonizing the definitions with the ones in the Small Vessel Regulations (i.e., engine power, personal watercraft), by extending liability to those who allow a person under 16 years of age to operate a personal watercraft, by allowing enforcement officers to stop an operator and require them to immediately produce proof of age, and by correcting a discrepancy between the English and French text.
